gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Hawks 127, Bucks 110
gameRecap.excerpt: The Hawks defeated the Bucks, 127-110. Trae Young recorded 20 points and 11 assists for the Hawks, while Giannis Antetokounmpo tallied 26 points and 11 rebounds for the Bucks in the losing effort. The Hawks improve to 1-2 on the season, while the Bucks fall to 1-1.
